original_title: SLPP May Day rally at Cambell Park
original_body_lines: Former President and SLPP Leader Mahinda Rajapaksa greets the crowd at the party’s May Day rally, which was held at Cambell Park today. Prime Minister Dinesh Gunawardene and MP Mahindananda Aluthgamage are also present. Pix by Waruna Wanniarachchi
